name: "I Don't Like This..." by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Various pens on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments, colors, and psychic surgery moshing.] I wasn't happy with how the experiment was progressing. I couldn't shift time. I couldn't phase thru walls. It was a near 100 percent failure---until I noticed the side effects... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
